<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA616_07_IH_0006_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <!-- <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema616_03_05.css" /> -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema616_07.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema616_07_ih_0006 paging">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="6_orange" class="is_star2" lang="y">모든 모서리의 길이의 합이 84 cm인 정육면체의 겉넓이는 몇 cm²인지 구하려고 합니다. 물음에 답해 보세요.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <article class="page page_1">
          <h3>정육면체의 한 모서리의 길이는 몇 cm인지 구해 보세요.</h3>
          <div class="question_box justify_center mt_20">
            <div class="input_wrap">
              <math-field data-answer-single="7" text-align="center"></math-field>
            </div>
            <span>cm</span>
          </div>

          <div class="solve_area">
            <div class="inner_solve">
              <div class="flex">
                <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
                <div class="conts_solve">
                  <p lang="y">정육면체의 모서리는 모두 12개입니다.</p>
                  <p lang="y" class="pl_40">➔ (한 모서리의 길이)=84÷12=7 (cm)</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="btn_area">
            <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
            <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
            <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- 2 page -->
        <article class="page page_2">
          <h3>정육면체의 겉넓이는 몇 cm²인지 구해 보세요.</h3>
          <div class="question_box justify_center">
            <div class="input_wrap">
              <math-field data-answer-single="294" text-align="center"></math-field>
            </div>
            <span>cm²</span>
          </div>
          <div class="solve_area">
            <div class="inner_solve">
              <div class="flex">
                <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
                <div class="conts_solve">
                  <p lang="y">(정육면체의 겉넓이)=7×7×6=294 (cm²)</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="btn_area">
            <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
            <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
            <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
          </div>
        </article>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
